    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AVOID THE PYRAMIDS!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/df3c6584cfecc3b212ceb9915f060c7f.poster.avif?t=1701314193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/df3c6584cfecc3b212ceb9915f060c7f.webm?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/df3c6584cfecc3b212ceb9915f060c7f.mp4?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>We are trying to escape from a dark and extremely disturbing mysterious place. We are trying to rescue our character, who has lost his memory and is waiting to be sacrificed, without getting caught by the enemies around and open the hidden areas of the room by exploring the surroundings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DON'T GET LOST IN THE MAZE!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/3a6f5b2eea99df07255d35c6c32ea112.poster.avif?t=1701314193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/3a6f5b2eea99df07255d35c6c32ea112.webm?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/3a6f5b2eea99df07255d35c6c32ea112.mp4?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Keep an eye on your stamina bar and choose where to run your character!<br>Make good use of the torch, which is our only friend and guide our way through the game, and try to explore the surroundings without getting caught by mysterious creatures! How long can you stay calm in this game that tests your stress and tension levels?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COLLECT THE EYES</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/01985329f832d10021471b49752689d2.poster.avif?t=1701314193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/01985329f832d10021471b49752689d2.webm?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/01985329f832d10021471b49752689d2.mp4?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight against 3 different types of enemies that will stress you out even more in the dark atmosphere!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GET RID OF THE CULT!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/97dba7b96cd1fd3a39cf4b276bd82275.poster.avif?t=1701314193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/97dba7b96cd1fd3a39cf4b276bd82275.webm?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401450/extras/97dba7b96cd1fd3a39cf4b276bd82275.mp4?t=1701314193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enjoy replayability thanks to the key that spawns in different locations each time you play!",
